  own declared minSdk 26-30 devices — a real "app doesn't launch" bug per
  this sprint's own success criteria. Own our window-background color
  instead, matching core:designsystem's brand palette so there's no visible
  flash-of-wrong-color before Compose's SpaceAntivirusTheme takes over.
-->
